    '<strong>Validation and field guidance</strong> — Bilingual tooltips explain names, contact details, address requirements and country formats directly at each field',
    '<strong>Log export and import</strong> — Request and Response Logs can be saved and restored as standardised JSON files',
    '<strong>Safer export decisions</strong> — An in-app dialog warns that exports may contain sensitive transaction and response data',
    '<strong>Merge or replace</strong> — Imports can extend the existing log or replace it completely',
